{"tid":806131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男童街頭賣雪條：我媽雀斑多 賺錢買面膜給她","createTime":"2018-09-04T11:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T12:17:08.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc0c3489f12995766d8aebcdfcadac128e228cb5","tid":806131,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"湖北武漢一對10歲和12歲的表兄弟，近日趁暑假「體驗生活」，在街頭賣懷舊綠豆雪條，每日收入可達100元(人民幣，下同)，其中表弟指，賺到的錢會用來買自己想要的東西，表哥卻表示，除了想用來買手機，還要買面膜給媽媽，因為她「雀斑太多」。有網民不禁揶揄「媽媽很感動，然後暴打了他」，亦有人大讚「貼心」、「孝順」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD%E8%B3%A3%E9%9B%AA%E6%A2%9D%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E5%AA%BD%E9%9B%80%E6%96%91%E5%A4%9A-%E8%B3%BA%E9%8C%A2%E8%B2%B7%E9%9D%A2%E8%86%9C%E7%B5%A6%E5%A5%B9-139057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E8%25A1%2597%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E9%259B%25AA%25E6%25A2%259D%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E9%259B%2580%25E6%2596%2591%25E5%25A4%259A-%25E8%25B3%25BA%25E9%258C%25A2%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%2586%259C%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E5%25A5%25B9-139057&d=mC2PSn5UZ7EsjR9XJG2kFC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=48c4ef1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD%E8%B3%A3%E9%9B%AA%E6%A2%9D%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E5%AA%BD%E9%9B%80%E6%96%91%E5%A4%9A-%E8%B3%BA%E9%8C%A2%E8%B2%B7%E9%9D%A2%E8%86%9C%E7%B5%A6%E5%A5%B9-139057</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73319c2e1f3873c2ca2577a8994713a9f7203864","tid":806131,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T12:06:31.000Z","msg":"香港男人：屌 咁細個就要畀家用"},{"pid":"175442cdd06f6c5f70b8879a61376a98d176c5c3","tid":806131,"uid":85427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73319c2e1f38